{"tid":1222936,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我們從甚麼時候開始獲得了人權 ?","createTime":"2019-06-14T14:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T00:54:52.000Z","uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2251ff8acae43983ef29251ccca7c4da77cb0c16","tid":1222936,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/85/Eleanor_Roosevelt_and_Human_Rights_Declaration.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F8%2F85%2FEleanor_Roosevelt_and_Human_Rights_Declaration.jpg&h=90e4bbee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>世界人權宣言，一份在二戰後，1948年由各國簽署的宣言，英美法中四國皆有參與簽訂，但並不具有法律效力。</strong><br />\n第一條：<br />\n<strong>人人生而自由，在尊嚴和權利上一律平等。他們賦有理性和良心，並應以兄弟關係的精神相對待。</strong><br />\n第九條：<br />\n<strong>任何人不得加以任意逮捕、拘禁或放逐。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/universal-declaration-human-rights/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Funiversal-declaration-human-rights%2Findex.html&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3Pjco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=da268404\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.un.org/en/universal-declaration-human-rights/index.html</a><br />\n鑒於篇幅會令大家TLDR，附上為完整公約內容，有興趣可以自行參詳。<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢份唔係公約，但影響後日兩份重要國際公約嘅簽署。分別係「公民及政治權利國際公約」以及「經濟、社會及文化權利國際公約」，各自確立咗世界公民嘅政治表達權利、同文化傳承權等等。<br />\n<br />\n自此宣言開始，各國開始簽訂各式各樣嘅人權公約。人，正式得到人權，我地生而是平等。<br />\n<br />\n以下列出幾項影響重大嘅公約/宣言：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>消除一切形式種族歧視國際公約</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ohchr.org/SiteCollectionImages/Bodies/CERD/50Years/banner_CERD_50_anniversary.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FSiteCollectionImages%2FBodies%2FCERD%2F50Years%2Fbanner_CERD_50_anniversary.jpg&h=b2005929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1969年1月4日生效。<br />\n約要求其締約國消除種族歧視和促進所有種族間的諒解。該公約也要求各國以法律禁止仇恨言論，並以刑事手段懲治種族主義組織。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>消除對婦女一切形式歧視公約(CEDAW)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://sfgov.org/dosw/sites/default/files/CEDAW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsfgov.org%2Fdosw%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FCEDAW.jpg&h=0414085d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1981年9月開始生效<br />\n該公約確立規則，保障婦女在政治、法律、工作、教育、醫療服務、商業活動和家庭關係等各方面的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>聯合國禁止酷刑公約</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://redress.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/convention-against-torture-and-other-cruel-inhuman-or-degrading-treatment-or-punishment.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fredress.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fconvention-against-torture-and-other-cruel-inhuman-or-degrading-treatment-or-punishment.jpg&h=8972e40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1984年開始生效<br />\n此公約防止世界上繼續存在有酷刑或其他相似的行為。該公約並要求各個締約國必須在其管轄的領域內，採取各種有效的方法避免酷刑的存在與發生，且禁止各締約國將人送回可能使該人遭受到酷刑的國家。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>兒童權利公約(CRC)</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://legal.un.org/avl/images/ha/crc/01-l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flegal.un.org%2Favl%2Fimages%2Fha%2Fcrc%2F01-l.jpg&h=397f1904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1990年9月2日開始生效<br />\n保障兒童在公民、經濟、政治、文化和社會中的權利。<br />\n《兒童權利公約》的四大基本原則維護兒童的權利：<br />\n生存權利、發展權利、參與權利、受保護權利。<br />\n<br />\n時至今時今日，絕大部份的先進國家，都嚴格遵守公約內容，維護公民權益，盡力令「人類」嘅生活係似翻個「人」。呢啲文本雖然只係幾張紙，除咗某啲宣揚階級觀念，打壓公民嘅極權國家之外，係各國嘅權力平衡、互相監督下，基本人權已經成為咗普世價值。"},{"pid":"91467dbb79c8ae1e42c120112cb3428e2662c7db","tid":1222936,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"你有基本人權嗎？"},{"pid":"0afc222ded4c9c045748b47b33d65acc91a4c396","tid":1222936,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"91467dbb79c8ae1e42c120112cb3428e2662c7db","tid":1222936,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"你有基本人權嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:17:12.000Z","msg":"現今世界，一切都係講資本，人權社會只係假象<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有錢，就有移民、屌屄、讀好學校、睇好醫生嘅人權<br />\n<br />\n冇錢，只有基本生存權"},{"pid":"51579e757e30a9e3ba23483aea250da3115f3c85","tid":1222936,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"你有生存權嗎 ?"},{"pid":"507e0fd006a50c3175b31442f3c7d797a40837c5","tid":1222936,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de90cac13c27eacce9e6a9cdfd793c3ba29c8a1a","tid":1222936,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:54:52.000Z","msg":"佢地當初其實點解要簡做人民公僕<br />\n市民先係佢地嘅老細<br />\n冇市民就冇佢地<br />\n佢地而家居然咁對我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}